Ing '''Sathyamangalam''' or '''Satyamangalam''' ([[Tamil language|Tamil]]:சத்தியமங்கலம்) metung yang lakanbalen o ciudad ampong metung a [[w:Municipality|municipality]] king [[Erode (distritu)]] king [[Estadu ampong teritoriu ning India|estadu]] ning [[Tamil Nadu]], [[India]].  Atiu king pangulu na ampong mauling pampang ning [[w:Bhavani River|Ilug Bhavani]], a mamagus papunta king [[w:Cauvery River|Kaveri]]. Ing Bannari Betta ing karinan ning templu nang Bannari Amma (metung a dios a Hindu), maki dayung 13 km ibat king balen ning Sathyamangalam.  

